OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day for much of England
OL,6,Fand Wales with hazy sunshine. Thicker
OL,7,Fcloud and outbreaks of rain will move
OL,8,Finto Scotland during the afternoon.
OL,9,FWindy in the north with gales
OL,10,Fdeveloping in northern Scotland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will sink south into
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland and northern England,
OL,14,Fwith strong winds. Staying largely dry
OL,15,Ffurther south with a few mist and fog
OL,16,Fpatches in southern England.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
