OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA wet and windy day for many,
OL,6,Fwith heavy, persistent rain across
OL,7,Fparts of northern England and Wales.
OL,8,FBlustery showers move into Scotland
OL,9,Fand Northern Ireland with hail and
OL,10,Fthunder.
